  "body": "<p>So excited about <a href=\"http://allisonkreft.typepad.com/\">Allison</a>'s new collaboration with <a href=\"http://websterspages.typepad.com/webstershome/2012/12/monday.html\">Webster's Pages</a>. Her designs have been some of my favorites for years, and these are no exception.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600319123438-T16B099QOD0A3WHHXEYS/7a-allisonpresentation-2-600x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>The papers are gorgeous - I had a chance to play with her new collection, including transparencies! The colors, icons and patterns are perfection. There's plenty of woodgrain, chevron, maps and cameras. Here's how this layout came together.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"7b-DSC_0705-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600319219435-1I76W2YG8NY9QYVV7VNJ/7b-DSC_0705-600x398.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"7c-DSC_0710-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600319232882-5SDZCZG0G1HMFIKNKKM0/7c-DSC_0710-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7d-DSC_0712-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600319170894-LVE5IYL7QX0H9XRZJ4QY/7d-DSC_0712-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7e-DSC_0715-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600319171026-949PEIMNLYENNV8ZCYRN/7e-DSC_0715-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7f-DSC_0716a-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600319171786-POM9HLOEAGZD5OM3VK8G/7f-DSC_0716a-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7g-AVerySpecialSunset-600x598.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600319171536-QQ51YKAX4OHPOR7456T6/7g-AVerySpecialSunset-600x598.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Other supplies: <a href=\"http://lifelovepaper.bigcartel.com/product/we-were-here-rubber-stamp\">We Were Here stamp</a> || <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/126954-white-amy-tangerine-sketchbook-journal-foam-thickers-stickers/%3Ffilters%3D_journal_thickers_\">Journal Thickers</a> || <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/studio-calico/131751-classic-calico-3-roller-date-stamp/%3Ffilters%3D_studio_calico_%252F_date_stamp_%252Fstamps\">Date Stamp</a> || <a href=\"http://scrapperin.blogspot.de/\">Scrapperin stamps</a> <strong>GIVEWAWAY:</strong> For your chance to win a collection pack from <a href=\"http://websterspages.typepad.com/\">Webster's Pages</a> of Allison Kreft's papers and assorted embellishments,<strong> </strong>leave a comment with your plans for the weekend. Random winner will be drawn on Monday, December 10 at 7am and a winner will be announced shortly after. <strong>Winner is #160 - christina rayevich! CONGRATS</strong></p>"
